## Interview-Focused Questions to Practice Daily
- What makes an API RESTful?
- Why should APIs be stateless?
- Why do we return 201 after create?
- What is the use of idempotency in PUT/DELETE?
- When should we return 400 vs 422?
- How do frontend and backend share data contracts?

---

## Common Mistakes to Avoid
- Using POST for every operation
- Returning 200 for all outcomes including errors
- Sending vague error messages
- Mixing entities directly in API responses
- Hardcoding URLs/tokens in Postman instead of variables
- Not testing negative scenarios

